			<char id="mars.gidrah.02.char">[stats:gidrah.mars.02.spec]</char>
			<char id="mars.tech-gidrah.char">these multi-legged killers move INCREDIBLY FAST! just being on the same planet gives me the jitters.</char>
		</story>
		<story qualifier="!automation" setting="mars.tech.setting">
