		</story>
		<story qualifier="automation,!robotics" setting="mars.tech.setting">
			<char id="mars.tech-left.char">commander, we must beseech you for more funding into ROBOTICS RESEARCH! i feel as if we are lagging behind in this area.</char>
		</story>
		<story qualifier="automation,robotics,!barracks" setting="mars.tech.setting">
